,"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T02:43:27.561+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":99,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://hurawatch.lol/","overview":"A young Indigenous game warden arrests an infamous poacher only to discover that the poacher knows the location of a plane carrying millions of dollars that has crashed in a frozen lake. When a group of criminals and dirty cops are alerted to the poacher’s whereabouts, the warden and the poacher team up to fight back and escape across the treacherous lake before the ice melts."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Ice Fall","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Un exmarine y cazador furtivo llamado Harlan (Joel Kinnaman) descubre un avión cargado con millones de dólares que ha caído en un lago congelado. Tras ser arrestado por una guardabosques nativa, un grupo de criminales y policías corruptos se enteran de su paradero. Por ello, Harlan y la ranger se unen para luchar e intentar escapar a través del peligroso lago antes de que el hielo se derrita."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Ледяной предел","runtime":88,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Харлан уже много лет бежит от своего прошлого и самого себя. В попытках оградиться от мира он поселился в резервации и стал настоящим отшельником. Но однажды он находит самолёт, потерпевший крушение, а в нём — миллионы долларов. Чтобы остаться в живых с таким сокровищем, Харлану придется пройти огонь и воду, но, возможно, именно навыки из его загадочного прошлого помогут ему выжить."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Крижаний драйв","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Молодій рейнджерці Ані вдається заарештувати відомого браконьєра Гарлана, який роками ховається від свого минулого. Та з’ясовується, що він знає про літак із мільйонами доларів, який розбився у замерзлому озері. Дорогою до відділку на них нападає банда, що полює за цими грошима. Тепер Ані та Гарлан змушені об’єднатися, щоб вижити серед дикої природи й утекти від переслідувачів. Але чи зможе вона довіритися йому, знаючи про його темне минуле?"},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"על קרח דק","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"על אגם קפוא בשמורה אינדיאנית באמריקה, שוטרת מקומית עוצרת צייד מסתורי, ומגלה שהוא יודע את מיקומו של מטוס הקבור תחת הקרח ונושא מיליוני דולרים. בדרך למעצר השניים מותקפים על ידי כנופיית שודדים, ונאלצים לשתף פעולה כדי לברוח מרודפיהם, ולשרוד מול הקרח הנמס שהולך ונהיה קטלני באותה המידה."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Ledo griūtis","runtime":96,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Jaunas vietinis gamtos apsaugos inspektorius sugauna pagarsėjusį brakonierių, tačiau netrukus paaiškėja, kad šis žino vietą, kur užšalusiame ežere guli sudužęs lėktuvas su milijonais dolerių. Kai apie šį lobį sužino nusikaltėlių gaujos ir korumpuoti pareigūnai, abu vyrai, anksčiau buvę priešininkai, priversti susivienyti. Kiekvienas žingsnis trapiu ledu tampa lenktynėmis su laiku – kol pavojai, godumas ir gamtos stichija nepribaigs jų pirmiau."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"Icefall – Tűz a jégen","runtime":0,"tagline":"Olvadó jég közepette megkezdődik a verseny a 7 millió dollárért!","homepage":"","overview":"Harlan (Joel Kinnaman), egy leszerelt deszantos, a modern világtól való teljes elzárkózásban talál menedéket: a hideg, végtelen pusztaság magányába vonul vissza Amerika északi részén, egy indián rezervátum elhagyatott tájain. Nem akar emberekkel találkozni, senkire sem támaszkodni – talán épp a múltja árnyai elől menekül. A világ azonban hamar utoléri. Egy nap rejtélyes módon lezuhant repülőgépre bukkan, tele milliókkal. A kísértésnek nehéz ellenállni – még nehezebb megtartani. Harlant elkapják, amikor Ani, a park fegyveres őreként szolgáló őslakos nő ráakad, és letartóztatja. Éppen bevinni készül a központba, amikor megjelenik a gép tulajdonosait képviselő csempészbanda – évek óta híján voltak a pénznek, és most követelik. Ani és Harlan kénytelenek félretenni a köztük lévő ellentétet. Összefognak, hogy túléljék a kegyetlen, fagyos tájat – és hogy megszerezzék a lezuhant vagyont önmaguknak.  (Csillag Lajos)"},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"شلال جليدي","runtime":99,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"يقوم حارس صيد شاب من السكان الأصليين بالقبض على صياد غير شرعي سيئ السمعة، ليكتشف أن هذا الصياد يعرف مكان طائرة تحمل ملايين الدولارات تحطمت في بحيرة متجمدة. عندما يتم إخطار مجموعة من المجرمين والشرطة الفاسدة بمكان الصياد، يتعاون الحارس والصياد لمواجهة الخطر والهروب عبر البحيرة الخطرة قبل أن يذوب الجليد."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"AE","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"ریزش یخ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"یک نگهبان محیط زیست جوان، یک شکارچی غیرمجاز بدنام را دستگیر می‌کند، اما به زودی متوجه می‌شود که آن شکارچی از محل سقوط یک هواپیما در یک دریاچه یخ‌زده که حامل میلیون‌ها دلار پول است..."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"Под леда","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Млад индиански надзирател арестува скандален бракониер, но скоро разбира, че той знае местоположението на самолет с милиони долари, който е катастрофирал в замръзнало езеро. Когато престъпници и корумпирани полицаи научават за местонахождението на бракониера, надзирателят и той обединяват сили, за да се защитят и да избягат през опасното езеро, преди ледът да се разтопи."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nuori alkuperäiskansojen taustan omaava metsänvartija pidättää pahamaineisen salametsästäjän, jolla on mukanaan salkullinen käteistä. Salametsästäjä kertoo salkun olevan peräisin jäätyneeseen järveen pudonneesta, käteisellä täytetystä lentokoneesta. He eivät kuitenkaan ole ainoita, jotka alkavat etsiä  konetta. Rikolliset, joiden ryöstösaalis on järven pohjassa, saavat huono-onnisen kaksikon kiinni. Kun korruptoituneet poliisitkin ovat juonessa mukana, he joutuvat vasten tahtoaan yhdistämään voimansa ja taistelemaan selviytyäkseen pakomatkasta sulavan jään yli."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"冰湖行动","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"一个犯罪团伙抢劫了二千万美元，运钞飞机却因为风暴掉进了冰湖。来年冰雪融化了，盗猎者哈兰在冰面上看到了一只带着金戒指的手，捡到了一皮箱钱。他一打开皮箱就触发了信号，犯罪团伙立马跟了过来。浑然不知的哈兰在冰上悠然的走，却被原住民护林员安妮逮住了，他无法解释钱来源，也没时间解释，犯罪团伙与腐败警察闻风而至，护林员与盗猎者被迫亡命组队，必须在冰面消融前穿越险恶冰湖，开展生死大逃亡，为守护宝藏展开绝地反击。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"아이스폴","runtime":0,"tagline":"녹아내리는 얼음 위, 700만 달러를 향한 죽음의 질주가 시작된다!","homepage":"","overview":"극한의 추위가 몰아치는 북미 오지. 젊은 야생동물 관리인이 베테랑 밀렵꾼을 체포하며 사건이 시작된다. 밀렵꾼은 우연히 얼어붙은 호수 아래 추락한 비행기와 수백만 달러의 현금이 있다는 엄청난 비밀을 털어놓는다.  현금의 소문은 순식간에 퍼지고, 부패한 경찰부터 무자비한 범죄자들까지 현장으로 몰려든다. 눈앞의 돈을 차지하려는 인간들의 욕망은 극에 달하고, 추락 지점인 위험천만한 얼음 호수는 삽시간에 아비규환으로 변한다.  언제 깨질지 모르는 살얼음판 위에서, 살아남기 위해 한 팀이 된 관리인과 밀렵꾼은 현금과 목숨을 건 최후의 생존 게임을 시작한다. 과연 그들은 서로를 믿고 이 얼음 지옥에서 탈출할 수 있을까?"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Een jonge inheemse jachtopziener arresteert een beruchte stroper en ontdekt dat deze de locatie kent van een vliegtuig vol miljoenen dollars dat is neergestort in een bevroren meer. Wanneer een groep criminelen en corrupte agenten lucht krijgt van de gevangenneming, moeten de jachtopziener en de stroper hun verschillen opzijzetten en samenwerken om te overleven. Terwijl het ijs onder hen langzaam begint te smelten, vechten ze terug tegen hun achtervolgers en proberen ze te ontsnappen over het verraderlijke meer."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"BE","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"冰湖行動","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"一個犯罪集團搶劫了二千萬美元，運鈔飛機卻因為風暴掉進了冰湖。來年冰雪融化了，盜獵者哈蘭在冰面上看到了一隻帶著金戒指的手，撿到了一皮箱錢。他一打開皮箱就觸發了信號，犯罪集團立刻跟了過來。渾然不知的哈蘭在冰上悠然的走，卻被原住民護林員安妮逮住了，他無法解釋錢來源，也沒時間解釋，犯罪集團與腐敗警察聞風而至，護林員與盜獵者被迫亡命組隊，必須在冰面消融前穿越險惡冰湖，開展生死大逃亡，為守護寶藏展開絕地反擊。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Un jove guardaboscos nadiu americà captura un famós caçador furtiu i descobreix que coneix la ubicació d'un avió que transporta milions de dòlars i que s'ha estavellat en un llac gelat."},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Een jonge inheemse jachtopziener arresteert een beruchte stroper. Daarna ontdekt de opzichter dat de stroper de geheime locatie kent van een neergestort vliegtuig dat miljoenen dollars bevat. Wanneer een groep criminelen en corrupte politiemannen te weten komt waar de stroper zich bevindt, vormen de opzichter en de stroper een onwaarschijnlijk team. Samen gaan ze door het gevaarlijke sneeuwlandschap op zoek naar hun prijs voordat het ijs onder hen smelt."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Icefall - Bis das Eis bricht","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ein junger indigener Wildhüter verhaftet einen berüchtigten Wilderer, nur um zu entdecken, dass der Wilderer den Standort eines Flugzeugs kennt, das Millionen von Dollar transportiert und in einem zugefrorenen See abgestürzt ist. Als eine Gruppe von Kriminellen und korrupten Polizisten auf den Aufenthaltsort des Wilderers aufmerksam wird, schließen sich der Wildhüter und der Wilderer zusammen, um zurückzuschlagen und über den tückischen See zu entkommen, bevor das Eis schmilzt."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"เจ้าหน้าที่พิทักษ์ป่าชาวพื้นเมืองอเมริกันหนุ่มที่จับพรานล่าสัตว์ที่โด่งดังได้ แต่กลับพบว่าพรานล่าสัตว์ผู้นี้รู้ตำแหน่งของเครื่องบินที่บรรทุกเงินหลายล้านดอลลาร์ที่ตกในทะเลสาบที่เป็นน้ำแข็ง"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Ghețuri blestemate","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"De ani buni, Harlan fuge de trecutul său și de el însuși. Ca să se izoleze de lume, s-a retras într-o rezervație și a devenit un adevărat proscris. Dar într-o zi descoperă un avion prăbușit, iar în interior, milioane de dolari. Înainte ca Harlan să poată revendica averea, este arestat de Ani, o tânără ranger. Însă, pe drumul spre secție, cei doi sunt atacați de Drake și banda lui, care caută de ani buni banii furați. Acum, Ani și Harlan trebuie să facă echipă ca să supraviețuiască în sălbăticie și să scape de urmăritorii lor nemiloși. Dar poate Ani să aibă încredere în Harlan, având în vedere trecutul lui misterios?"},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Un garde-chasse autochtone arrête un braconnier qui sait où se trouve une cachette avec des millions de dollars. Traqué par des criminels et des flics corrompus, les deux doivent faire équipe pour trouver l'argent avant eux et pour s'échapper à travers un lac en dégel."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Un exmarine y cazador furtivo llamado Harlan (Joel Kinnaman) descubre un avión cargado con millones de dólares que ha caído en un lago congelado. Tras ser arrestado por una guardabosques nativa, un grupo de criminales y policías corruptos se enteran de su paradero. Por ello, Harlan y la ranger se unen para luchar e intentar escapar a través del peligroso lago antes de que el hielo se derrita."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"A história gira em torno de um guarda florestal nativo americano, que captura um famoso caçador apenas para descobrir que ele sabe a localização de um avião que transportava milhões de dólares e que caiu em um lago congelado."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"ყინულცვენა","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"Lodowa pułapka","runtime":96,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Gdy strażniczka Annie zatrzymuje kłusownika, nie spodziewa się, że ich życie wkrótce się zmieni. Oboje trafiają na celownik bezwzględnego gangu, który zrobi wszystko by zdobyć pieniądze. Rozpoczyna się brutalna walka o życie na wielkim zamarzniętym jeziorze, gdzie każdy fałszywy krok może być tym ostatnim."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ein junger indigener Wildhüter verhaftet einen berüchtigten Wilderer, nur um zu entdecken, dass der Wilderer den Standort eines Flugzeugs kennt, das Millionen von Dollar transportiert und in einem zugefrorenen See abgestürzt ist. Als eine Gruppe von Kriminellen und korrupten Polizisten auf den Aufenthaltsort des Wilderers aufmerksam wird, schließen sich der Wildhüter und der Wilderer zusammen, um zurückzuschlagen und über den tückischen See zu entkommen, bevor das Eis schmilzt."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"AT","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ein junger indigener Wildhüter verhaftet einen berüchtigten Wilderer, nur um zu entdecken, dass der Wilderer den Standort eines Flugzeugs kennt, das Millionen von Dollar transportiert und in einem zugefrorenen See abgestürzt ist. Als eine Gruppe von Kriminellen und korrupten Polizisten auf den Aufenthaltsort des Wilderers aufmerksam wird, schließen sich der Wildhüter und der Wilderer zusammen, um zurückzuschlagen und über den tückischen See zu entkommen, bevor das Eis schmilzt."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"CH","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Příběh se točí kolem mladého indiánského strážce, který dopadne notorického pytláka, aby pak zjistil, že pytlák ví o místě, kde se v zamrzlém jezeře nachází letadlo s miliony dolarů."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[],"similar_content":[{"id":232,"adult":false,"title":"Rumble Fish","video":false,"overview":"Absent-minded street thug Rusty James struggles to live up to his legendary older brother's reputation, and longs for the days of gang warfare.","genre_ids":[80,18,10749],"popularity":3.2587,"vote_count":745,"poster_path":"/nwIUWs7cexC8Wk9c6ey8nFltAZd.jpg","release_date":"1983-10-09","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/g2SvOk7ZEgV1VyOfJB2CwFyqgmF.jpg","original_title":"Rumble Fish","original_language":"en"},{"id":856,"adult":false,"title":"Who Framed Roger Rabbit","video":false,"overview":"'Toon star Roger is worried that his wife Jessica is playing pattycake with someone else, so the studio hires detective Eddie Valiant to snoop on her. But the stakes are quickly raised when Marvin Acme is found dead and Roger is the prime suspect.","genre_ids":[14,16,35,80],"popularity":6.2205,"vote_count":6070,"poster_path":"/lYfRc57Kx9VgLZ48iulu0HKnM15.jpg","release_date":"1988-06-22","vote_average":7.531,"backdrop_path":"/udIE8Cdon9wnYmVIOFYrBPfA2Mq.jpg","original_title":"Who Framed Roger Rabbit","original_language":"en"},{"id":871,"adult":false,"title":"Planet of the Apes","video":false,"overview":"Astronaut Taylor crash lands on a distant planet ruled by apes who use a primitive race of humans for experimentation and sport. Soon Taylor finds himself among the hunted, his life in the hands of a benevolent chimpanzee scientist.","genre_ids":[878,12,18,28],"popularity":7.1507,"vote_count":3855,"poster_path":"/2r9iKnlSYEk4daQadsXfcjHfIjQ.jpg","release_date":"1968-02-07","vote_average":7.645,"backdrop_path":"/gmJOXle5QeOOVFEYOVBOkmIJUWV.jpg","original_title":"Planet of the Apes","original_language":"en"},{"id":1452198,"adult":false,"title":"Hamburg","video":false,"overview":"Germán is a driver and transports women who work as slaves in brothels on the Costa del Sol. Broke and lost, he tries to get by working for his friend Cacho, who manages several of these clubs for a local mafia. One night he is presented with what seems like a chance to change his life, but this decision will put him in more danger than ever. He has only one option left, the same one Alina thinks of every night: to escape.","genre_ids":[53],"popularity":0.2426,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/aWghdaaHi1TKab5Esf25XhxnxcN.jpg","release_date":"2025-05-30","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Hamburgo","original_language":"es"},{"id":1422,"adult":false,"title":"The Departed","video":false,"overview":"To take down South Boston's Irish Mafia, the police send in one of their own to infiltrate the underworld, not realizing the syndicate has done likewise. While an undercover cop curries favor with the mob kingpin, a career criminal rises through the police ranks. But both sides soon discover there's a mole among them.","genre_ids":[18,53,80],"popularity":10.8185,"vote_count":15909,"poster_path":"/nT97ifVT2J1yMQmeq20Qblg61T.jpg","release_date":"2006-10-04","vote_average":8.16,"backdrop_path":"/6WRrGYalXXveItfpnipYdayFkQB.jpg","original_title":"The Departed","original_language":"en"},{"id":9504,"adult":false,"title":"Glengarry Glen Ross","video":false,"overview":"Times are tough at Premiere Properties. Shelley \"the machine\" Levene and Dave Moss are veteran salesmen, but only Ricky Roma is on a hot streak. The new Glengarry sales leads could turn everything around, but the front office is holding them back until these \"losers\" prove themselves. Then someone decides to take matters into his own hands, stealing the Glengarry leads and leaving everyone wondering who did it.","genre_ids":[80,18,9648],"popularity":2.749,"vote_count":1554,"poster_path":"/zcaEDx8KlVfh4vKfMNLhiSi5Oz4.jpg","release_date":"1992-09-10","vote_average":7.329,"backdrop_path":"/qukaw3P4MOFNdxjhNpClhT9unr8.jpg","original_title":"Glengarry Glen Ross","original_language":"en"},{"id":14164,"adult":false,"title":"Dragonball Evolution","video":false,"overview":"On his 18th birthday, Goku receives a mystical Dragonball as a gift from his grandfather. There are only six others like it in the whole world, and legend has it that whoever possesses all seven will be granted one perfect wish. When the arrival of a dark force triggers a tragedy, Goku and his companions are propelled into an epic quest to collect the seven Dragonballs and save the Earth from destruction.","genre_ids":[28,12,14,878,53],"popularity":2.4817,"vote_count":2169,"poster_path":"/sunS9xhPnFNP5wlOWrvbpBteAB.jpg","release_date":"2009-03-12","vote_average":2.936,"backdrop_path":"/19ChHftp06sllxdgINPSTDIyKHw.jpg","original_title":"Dragonball Evolution","original_language":"en"},{"id":103,"adult":false,"title":"Taxi Driver","video":false,"overview":"Suffering from insomnia, disturbed loner Travis Bickle takes a job as a New York City cabbie, haunting the streets nightly, growing increasingly detached from reality as he dreams of cleaning up the filthy city.","genre_ids":[80,18],"popularity":12.5381,"vote_count":13203,"poster_path":"/ekstpH614fwDX8DUln1a2Opz0N8.jpg","release_date":"1976-02-09","vote_average":8.129,"backdrop_path":"/9uddYYTNcLWpzUkl5iw1RUYhLhY.jpg","original_title":"Taxi Driver","original_language":"en"},{"id":283601,"adult":false,"title":"Galveston","video":false,"overview":"After a violent encounter, Roy finds Rocky and sees something in her eyes that prompts a fateful decision. He takes her with him as he flees to Galveston, an action as ill-advised as it is inescapable.","genre_ids":[53],"popularity":1.3915,"vote_count":535,"poster_path":"/u3hDPc70JEWbrLruk6sni1OcODe.jpg","release_date":"2018-10-10","vote_average":6.117,"backdrop_path":"/sX8QB6p9nTltEnKLiFE2lXad7cc.jpg","original_title":"Galveston","original_language":"en"},{"id":13715,"adult":false,"title":"At Close Range","video":false,"overview":"Brad Whitewood Jr. lives in rural Pennsylvania and has few prospects. Against his mother's wishes, he seeks out his estranged father, the head of a gang of thieves in a nearby town. Though his new girlfriend supports his criminal ambitions, Brad Jr. soon learns that his father is a dangerous man. Inspired by the real events that led to the end of the Johnston Gang, who operated in the northeastern United States in the 1970s.","genre_ids":[80,18,53],"popularity":1.8145,"vote_count":298,"poster_path":"/bOkXqMmLowHBZY9lptWi3ljOXx4.jpg","release_date":"1986-04-18","vote_average":6.809,"backdrop_path":"/ceFgHH7mnpwrKoK8dVRjfvIVr5e.jpg","original_title":"At Close Range","original_language":"en"},{"id":1463298,"adult":false,"title":"Vengeance in the Dreary Night","video":false,"overview":"Jefri and Sarah are an adulterous couple now desperately trying to create an alibi after the corpse of Sofia, the lawful wife they murdered, mysteriously disappears from the morgue. Arya Pradana, a police investigator, uses all his logic to uncover the truth. Has the corpse come back to life to take revenge on her killers?","genre_ids":[80,18,9648,53],"popularity":0.6319,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/eichIZLd7e9AgYltckEwWgrFQcq.jpg","release_date":"2025-05-28","vote_average":7.25,"backdrop_path":"/p1V67T5vf7HD91BVe4K9TUZHtl4.jpg","original_title":"Dendam Malam Kelam","original_language":"id"},{"id":667177,"adult":false,"title":"Dead Earth","video":false,"overview":"Two young women's plans to try to live a normal life in isolation after a world ending apocalypse go awry when they are discovered.","genre_ids":[28,18,27,53],"popularity":0.5539,"vote_count":24,"poster_path":"/dTEY7mDBVwYnByLJaJKcC4areCG.jpg","release_date":"2020-01-28","vote_average":3.333,"backdrop_path":"/jF3gk9a4t8JH0MaCCVxkXldKVDJ.jpg","original_title":"Dead Earth","original_language":"en"},{"id":12223,"adult":false,"title":"The Stepford Wives","video":false,"overview":"Joanna Eberhart comes to the town of Stepford, Connecticut with her family, but soon discovers there lies a sinister truth in the all too perfect behavior of the female residents.","genre_ids":[9648,53,878,27],"popularity":4.4694,"vote_count":351,"poster_path":"/5z1ogJJmQkCoU62VJmut4nnc2qs.jpg","release_date":"1975-02-12","vote_average":6.682,"backdrop_path":"/pgVTwsJXv1i2GGZ2yB7KfiYqGAc.jpg","original_title":"The Stepford Wives","original_language":"en"},{"id":575,"adult":false,"title":"The Experiment","video":false,"overview":"20 volunteers agree to take part in a seemingly well-paid experiment advertised by the university. It is supposed to be about aggressive behavior in an artificial prison situation. A journalist senses a story behind the ad and smuggles himself in among the test subjects. They are randomly divided into prisoners and guards. What seems like a game at the beginning soon turns into bloody seriousness.","genre_ids":[18,53],"popularity":2.0421,"vote_count":1183,"poster_path":"/mfxXel8k2UWkgJ4MIsvVBsqnvFp.jpg","release_date":"2001-03-08","vote_average":7.412,"backdrop_path":"/6LrSj1vsYALVLTf2RCCfJFWimM7.jpg","original_title":"Das Experiment","original_language":"de"},{"id":1538,"adult":false,"title":"Collateral","video":false,"overview":"Cab driver Max picks up a man who offers him $600 to drive him around. But the promise of easy money sours when Max realizes his fare is an assassin.","genre_ids":[18,80,53],"popularity":6.3378,"vote_count":6124,"poster_path":"/nV5316WUsVij8sVXLCF1g7TFitg.jpg","release_date":"2004-08-04","vote_average":7.238,"backdrop_path":"/lEfZFNs5hr1Pgn4vpb7X31J927x.jpg","original_title":"Collateral","original_language":"en"},{"id":9946,"adult":false,"title":"End of Days","video":false,"overview":"Cynical bodyguard Jericho is hired by a man possessed by Satan, who is in search of his bride. When Jericho realizes what is happening, he must do everything he can to save the woman and the world.","genre_ids":[28,27,14],"popularity":2.9467,"vote_count":1992,"poster_path":"/pY8FbKKl3VD0jRI1iDFrwN6alLa.jpg","release_date":"1999-11-24","vote_average":6.082,"backdrop_path":"/oVp4NyyOqVPKrv5PBA7Sjwoh09S.jpg","original_title":"End of Days","original_language":"en"},{"id":10173,"adult":false,"title":"Marked for Death","video":false,"overview":"Just retired from the Drug Enforcement Agency, John Hatcher returns to his hometown and quickly discovers that drugs have infiltrated his old neighborhood. Determined to drive the dealers out, Hatcher crosses paths with a ferocious Jamaican drug lord who vows that Hatcher and his family are now marked for death.","genre_ids":[28,80,18,53],"popularity":2.5204,"vote_count":574,"poster_path":"/xYaetJsSm5FC1zxhdW8UR1NVXzc.jpg","release_date":"1990-10-05","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/rCTf5W1531LiFxJzUhdAcV9EDav.jpg","original_title":"Marked for Death","original_language":"en"},{"id":10410,"adult":false,"title":"Hoffa","video":false,"overview":"A portrait of union leader James R. Hoffa, as seen through the eyes of his friend, Bobby Ciaro. The film follows Hoffa through his countless battles with the RTA and President Roosevelt.","genre_ids":[80,36,18],"popularity":3.6223,"vote_count":347,"poster_path":"/aMGhaSkhkFwz33hKEsBrJ3ptx3g.jpg","release_date":"1992-12-25","vote_average":6.251,"backdrop_path":"/dineJzDZLuEXNNy261vFcJgqhxr.jpg","original_title":"Hoffa","original_language":"en"},{"id":335077,"adult":false,"title":"Battle For SkyArk","video":false,"overview":"In the near future the earth has become desolate and dangerous. Now inhabited by by a mysterious race of creatures, humanity has been forced to find refuge in the SkyArk, a man-made city in the sky. As the population grows, space becomes scarce and only the rich and powerful can stay, dumping the poor and orphaned of SkyArk to the abandoned earth.","genre_ids":[10751,878,28,12],"popularity":0.4351,"vote_count":69,"poster_path":"/cb2t0c07LP2lmP1URmXB3AUMWdq.jpg","release_date":"2015-05-18","vote_average":3.8,"backdrop_path":"/zneUwXxrEckzW87ggCJ1eBK8uYN.jpg","original_title":"Battle For SkyArk","original_language":"en"},{"id":520763,"adult":false,"title":"A Quiet Place Part II","video":false,"overview":"Following the events at home, the Abbott family now face the terrors of the outside world. Forced to venture into the unknown, they realize that the creatures that hunt by sound are not the only threats that lurk beyond the sand path.","genre_ids":[878,53,27],"popularity":7.1816,"vote_count":7217,"poster_path":"/4q2hz2m8hubgvijz8Ez0T2Os2Yv.jpg","release_date":"2021-05-21","vote_average":7.441,"backdrop_path":"/am782sUaTOGcEPEdUUjybwUZP1f.jpg","original_title":"A Quiet Place Part II","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt29780866","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q125627194","instagram_id":null,"metacritic_id":"movie/icefall","mydramalist_id":"397522","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/icefall"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":108804,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"AU","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"20